steps.instruction:
### Prep
- Zest the three oranges (no white in the zest, about 1 teaspoon)
- Peel Oranges and cut into segments; squeeze membranes (about 1/2 cup of juice)
- Cut the fennel in half lengthwise; slice fennel, white part only (about 2 cups)


### Steps
1. Combine all ingredients (other than spring mix and almonds) in a salad bowl
2. Add spring mix and toss to coat evenly
3. Top with almonds and serve
